Description: Orbital Network Infrastructure - Decentralized Web
 ONI is a peer-to-peer internet network that replaces traditional web
 infrastructure with a fully decentralized alternative. Includes:
 .
 - ONI Manager: Desktop GUI for managing nodes, domains, and hosting
 - Orbit Browser: Desktop browser for the orb:// protocol and .orb domains
 - ONI P2P Node: Peer-to-peer networking layer
 - ONS Server: Decentralized DNS for .orb domain resolution
 - Domain Registrar: Free .orb domain registration
 - Docker support: Self-hosting via docker-compose
 .
 The People's Internet - Decentralized, Free, Open Source.